# .graphifyignore — files excluded from the knowledge graph.
# gitignore syntax. Root = this docs/ folder (run graphify here).

# Scraper metadata (not content) — corrupts the graph.
manifest.json

# Index / listing / hub pages — no real content, create false hub nodes.
index.md
blog.md
blog-all-posts.md
fs-site.md
blog-category-*.md
blog-author-*.md

# Aggregate duplicate of the individual help-faq-*.md pages.
help-faq-all.md

# Locale-duplicate careers listing (Spanish "all positions").
blog-todos-los-puestos*.md

# Micro release-notes (463 files, ~43% of corpus): tiny, repetitive,
# low semantic value — would dominate the graph with near-identical nodes.
blog-changelog-*.md

# Hiring posts + meetup event pages — not product/docs knowledge.
careers*.md
makers-meetup*.md
